    {
      "start": 486.65,
      "end": 488.23,
      "text": "that is hardest to contemplate"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.23,
      "end": 490.25,
      "text": "about our society and ourselves"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.25,
      "end": 493.26,
      "text": "Mothers cannot help but be in touch"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.26,
